  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Branch Manager",
  "description": "<p>With over <strong>20 years of trusted brand heritage</strong>, BazGym is one of Singapore’s leading gymnastics and movement education providers for children and families. As we continue to grow, we are looking for a <strong>passionate, driven, organised, and people-focused Branch Manager</strong> to lead one of our centres.</p><h3>🏅 Your Role</h3><p>As Branch Manager, you will be responsible for the <strong>overall performance and smooth operations</strong> of the branch, working closely with coaches, admin staff, and headquarters.</p><p>Key responsibilities include:</p><ul><li><p>Overseeing <strong>student enrolment, retention, and customer experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Managing and motivating <strong>coaching and admin teams</strong></p></li><li><p>Ensuring <strong>high teaching standards</strong>, safety, and programme quality</p></li><li><p>Monitoring <strong>attendance, staff morale, and team development</strong></p></li><li><p>Overseeing <strong>accurate and timely school fee invoicing and collection</strong></p></li><li><p>Maintaining <strong>branch image, cleanliness, and professionalism</strong></p></li><li><p>Supporting and organising <strong>company events, carnivals, and outreach activities</strong></p></li><li><p>Working with senior management to <strong>grow the branch and strengthen the BazGym brand</strong></p></li></ul>",
